title: TEST BURN DAO
body:
Proposed amount to burn: 9000000000000 SHIBBY

How to verify the proposed DAO transaction :

Copy the value from the field "Data". This is the encoded contract call (XXXXXXXXX)
Open https://cleanunicorn.github.io/santoku/#/ to decode it
2.2 Paste the copied value into "Encoded ABI)
2.3 Click on the checkbox "ABI"
2.4 open bscscan, go to the SHIBBY contract and copy the ABI
2.5 Paste the ABI into the textfield "ABI"
2.6 click "Decode"
2.7 verify "address _to" (recipient) and "_value" (amount)
